{"Id":705123,"Title":"兰陵王•春夜病中听雨","Dynasty":"清","Author":"沈谦","Context":"晚风厉。十二帘拢垂地。灯忽暗，不许结花，镇日撩人有何喜。小鬟熏素被。耿耿全无睡意。帘纤雨，却又打窗，问道三更过还未。寻思转无味。怎偏我逢春，愁病相继。红桥曲巷迷征骑。曾持酒低劝，写词偷和，宝钗拨火人半醉。恁时节将睡。憔悴。更腰细。那枕上莺声，何日相慰。枝头春色今馀几。怕粉蕊湮透，檀心滴碎。苍天何恨，也有恁，许多泪。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"兰陵王","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"af178062b3304475466d394322bb2826","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5777199,"Sentence":"晚风厉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǎn fēng lì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777200,"Sentence":"十二帘拢垂地。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shǐ èr lián lǒng chuǐ 地","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777202,"Sentence":"小鬟熏素被。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiǎo huán xūn sù bèi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777203,"Sentence":"耿耿全无睡意。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gěng gěng quán mó shuì yì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777205,"Sentence":"寻思转无味。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xún sāi zhuǎi mó wèi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777209,"Sentence":"恁时节将睡。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nèn shǐ jiē jiāng shuì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777210,"Sentence":"憔悴。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiáo cuì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":11,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777211,"Sentence":"更腰细。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gēng yāo xì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777201,"Sentence":"灯忽暗，不许结花，镇日撩人有何喜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dēng hū àn ，bú hǔ jiē huā ，zhēn rì liāo rén yǒu hé xi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5777204,"Sentence":"帘纤雨，却又打窗，问道三更过还未。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lián qiàn yǔ ，què yòu dá chuāng ，wèn dāo sān gēng guō hái wèi